flowchart LR
  IN[Input - payable item with readiness outcome from Spend]
  WB[Workbench - select and prepare batch - UI only]
  SCH[Schedule - persisted execution status Scheduled]
  EXE[Execute or register paid - persisted execution status Executed or Paid]
  OUT[Outputs - cash truth record and downstream visibility]

  IN --> WB --> SCH --> EXE --> OUT

  subgraph Guardrails[Guardrails]
    G1[Queue does not form readiness - it consumes readiness]
    G2[Selected or prepared is not equal to scheduled]
    G3[Scheduled is not equal to executed or paid]
  end

  IN -.-> G1
  WB -.-> G2
  SCH -.-> G3
